reviewText: It was nice to see some of the "So You Think You Can Dance"  folks in it. I appreciated the flow of the movie and the outcome. Most of all It shows we under estimate friendship and resources that are right in front of us most of the time. Never let someone tell us they like us then change the us they like to fit their groove. If they do or try to  then the initial like was a Lie.
Outstanding Dance movie with a good story.
I love the movie especially because Les Twins are in it
Bought it for Robert Roldan, so it was exactly what I wanted.
If you like the Step Up series, you will like this
